trans-unit.source: Represents a set of query parameters that can be passed to a personalization provider using the various get and find methods.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et sett med spørringsparametere som kan sendes til en leverandør av personlige data ved hjelp av forskjellige get og finne metoder.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: This class is used as a parameter value for various get and find methods of a personalization provider, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.FindState%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.GetCountOfState%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes som en parameterverdi for ulike get og finne metoder for en leverandør av personlige data, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.FindState%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.GetCountOfState%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.GetCountOfState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.FindState%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default indexer allows generic access to the query parameters maintained by this object.
trans-unit.target: Standard indekserer gir generisk tilgang til spørringsparametere vedlikeholdes av dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: The three properties that are explicitly exposed by this class, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.PathToMatch%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UserInactiveSinceDate%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UsernameToMatch%2A>, are stored using query key values that are the same as the property names of this class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene tre som eksplisitt vises av denne klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.PathToMatch%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UserInactiveSinceDate%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UsernameToMatch%2A>lagres spørringen nøkkelverdiene som er lik egenskapsnavn av denne klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UsernameToMatch%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UserInactiveSinceDate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.PathToMatch%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.Item%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.Item%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A instance of this class is used as a parameter value for various get and find methods of a personalization provider, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.FindState%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.GetCountOfState%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av denne klassen brukes som en parameterverdi for ulike get og finne metoder for en leverandør av personlige data, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.FindState%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.GetCountOfState%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.GetCountOfState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationProvider.FindState%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the query parameter.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdien for Spørringsparameteren.

trans-unit.source: This property is the default indexer for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er standard indekserer for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery>

trans-unit.source: It returns the value of the query parameter indicated by `queryKey`.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer verdien for Spørringsparameteren angitt av `queryKey`.

trans-unit.source: You can use `PersonalizationStateQuery.this["UsernameToMatch"]`, `PersonalizationStateQuery.this["PathToMatch"]` and `PersonalizationStateQuery.this["UserInactiveSinceDate"]` to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UsernameToMatch%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.PathToMatch%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UserInactiveSinceDate%2A> properties, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke `PersonalizationStateQuery.this["UsernameToMatch"]`, `PersonalizationStateQuery.this["PathToMatch"]` og `PersonalizationStateQuery.this["UserInactiveSinceDate"]` til å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UsernameToMatch%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.PathToMatch%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UserInactiveSinceDate%2A>Egenskaper henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UserInactiveSinceDate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.PathToMatch%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationStateQuery.UsernameToMatch%2A>

trans-unit.source: When these three properties are set in the indexer, they are validated against the proper type.
trans-unit.target: Når disse tre egenskapene er angitt i indeksering, valideres mot av riktig type.

trans-unit.source: This property returns `null` if `queryKey` does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer `null` Hvis `queryKey` finnes ikke.

trans-unit.source: A case-insensitive query string.
trans-unit.target: En samlingstype spørringsstreng.

trans-unit.source: The value should be one of the following: "PathToMatch", "UserInactiveSinceDate", or "UsernameToMatch".
trans-unit.target: Verdien må være én av følgende: "PathToMatch", "UserInactiveSinceDate" eller "UsernameToMatch".

trans-unit.source: The value of the query parameter indicated by the queryKey parameter.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for Spørringsparameteren angitt av den queryKey parameteren.

trans-unit.source: queryKey is .
trans-unit.target: queryKeyis .

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path to be used for a query.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banen som skal brukes for en spørring.

trans-unit.source: This property contains a path to match when executing queries.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen inneholder en bane som samsvarer med under utføring av spørringer.

trans-unit.source: If PathToMatch contains wildcard characters, they are passed through to the underlying data store.
trans-unit.target: Hvis PathToMatch inneholder jokertegn, skal de sendes til den underliggende datakilden.

trans-unit.source: This property can be set to `null`, indicating that a query should not filter based on path.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan settes til `null`, som angir at en spørring ikke kan filtrere basert på banen.

trans-unit.source: If this property is non-`null`, its value is trimmed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er ikke -`null`, verdien beskjæres.

trans-unit.source: The path to be used for a query.
trans-unit.target: Banen som skal brukes for en spørring.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the last active date used in a query.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den siste aktive datoen som brukes i en spørring.

trans-unit.source: This property indicates the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.UserPersonalizationStateInfo.LastActivityDate%2A> property to filter against.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.UserPersonalizationStateInfo.LastActivityDate%2A>til å filtrere mot.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.UserPersonalizationStateInfo.LastActivityDate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The exact comparison is to include records where the value of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.UserPersonalizationStateInfo.LastActivityDate%2A> is less than or equal to the value of the UserInactiveSinceDate property.
trans-unit.target: Nøyaktige sammenligningen er inneholder poster der verdien av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.UserPersonalizationStateInfo.LastActivityDate%2A>er mindre enn eller lik verdien for egenskapen UserInactiveSinceDate.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.UserPersonalizationStateInfo.LastActivityDate%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property can be set to <xref:System.DateTime.MaxValue>, indicating that a query should not filter based on the last activity date.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan settes til <xref:System.DateTime.MaxValue>, som angir at en spørring ikke kan filtrere basert på den siste Aktivitetsdatoen.</xref:System.DateTime.MaxValue>

trans-unit.source: The last active date to be used in a query.
trans-unit.target: Den siste aktive datoen som skal brukes i en spørring.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the user name in a query.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir brukernavnet i en spørring.

trans-unit.source: This property represents the user name to filter against when executing a query.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen representerer brukernavnet for å filtrere mot under utføring av en spørring.

trans-unit.source: If UsernameToMatch contains wildcard characters, they are passed through to the underlying data store.
trans-unit.target: Hvis UsernameToMatch inneholder jokertegn, skal de sendes til den underliggende datakilden.

trans-unit.source: This property can be set to `null`, indicating that a query should not filter based on the user name.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan settes til `null`, som angir at en spørring ikke kan filtrere basert på brukernavnet.

trans-unit.source: If this property is non-`null`, its value is trimmed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er ikke -`null`, verdien beskjæres.

trans-unit.source: The user name to be used in a query.
trans-unit.target: Navnet som skal brukes i en spørring.
